name: Cheeseburger
description: A delicious cheeseburger with a juicy beef patty, cheese, lettuce, tomato, and special sauce.

name: Pepperoni Pizza
description: A classic pepperoni pizza with a crispy crust, tangy tomato sauce, and melted mozzarella cheese.

name: Chicken Nuggets
description: Crispy and golden chicken nuggets served with your choice of dipping sauce.

name: French Fries
description: Classic french fries, crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, seasoned to perfection.

name: Caesar Salad
description: Fresh romaine lettuce, croutons, and Parmesan cheese tossed in a creamy Caesar dressing.

name: BBQ Chicken Sandwich
description: Grilled chicken breast with BBQ sauce, lettuce, tomato, and onions on a toasted bun.

name: Veggie Burger
description: A hearty veggie burger made with black beans, corn, and spices, topped with lettuce and tomato.

name: Hot Dog
description: A classic hot dog with your choice of toppings: ketchup, mustard, onions, and relish.

name: Chocolate Milkshake
description: A rich and creamy chocolate milkshake made with real ice cream and topped with whipped cream.

name: Fish Tacos
description: Soft tortillas filled with crispy fish, cabbage slaw, and a tangy lime sauce.
